{"tid":841632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沖繩縣知事選舉 美軍之子反美軍基地","createTime":"2018-09-29T16:05:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T16:11:42.000Z","uid":28765,"like":17,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"b0ac4569cf86f54387696486a824ee8dcec9cd04","tid":841632,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T16:05:01.000Z","msg":"2018-09-29 22:29聯合報 記者莊蕙嘉╱即時報導<br />\n<br />\n日本沖繩縣30日舉行知事選舉，民調領先的候選人玉城丹尼被自民黨視為主要對手。<br />\n<br />\n58歲的玉城身世特別，本名玉城康裕，父親是沖繩基地美軍，和擔任服務生的女子相遇。玉城母親懷孕時，父親返回美國，臨行前為未出世兒子取名「丹尼斯」（Dennis）。但他父親未再回到日本，母親生下他後獨力撫養。<br />\n<br />\n玉城有混血外貌，骨子裡卻是道地沖繩人。他曾主持廣播節目，一口流利的方言讓他廣受沖繩長者喜愛。2002年他參選沖繩市議員，創下史上最高得票數紀錄，2005年參選眾議員失敗，2009年第二度挑戰順利當選。<br />\n<br />\n上月初病逝的沖繩知事翁長雄志曾為玉城站台，他也在翁長病逝後宣布「繼承遺志」，競選主軸堅定反對美軍基地搬遷至名護市，更反對美軍基地留在沖繩。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/09/29/realtime/5331241.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F09%2F29%2Frealtime%2F5331241.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600%26exp%3D3600&h=59ef03e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n玉城丹尼喊出「把藍天還給沖繩兒童」，反對美軍基地。（取自推特）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/09/29/realtime/5331242.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F09%2F29%2Frealtime%2F5331242.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600%26exp%3D3600&h=70107544&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n玉城（左）競選眾議員時，翁長雄志（右）曾為他站台。（取自推特）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://money.udn.com/money/story/5599/3394749\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoney.udn.com%2Fmoney%2Fstory%2F5599%2F3394749&d=%2FYj1B1gVb%2BCtfA9wV4ZofjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=9b67e3ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://money.udn.com/money/story/5599/3394749</a>"},{"pid":"fc7fabfd9418f4e8c19b7568b9e3c8f764f6b9da","tid":841632,"uid":22974,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T21:57:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b1beeca337ce5c831895cee2947d2ec248f697e9","tid":841632,"uid":51701,"like":29,"dislike":4,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T22:15:07.000Z","msg":"負皮做乜鳩<br />\n根本沖繩人真係食晒軍營衰野而冇[補償]<br />\n日軍仲迫過佢地自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n夾係中間真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2e3de933a55761022d3f7cbf0af5b6c53109711","tid":841632,"uid":52595,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T22:46:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f3dfca2cf90abb5730c5ab8f5a7509c730d52534","tid":841632,"uid":96743,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T22:56:28.000Z","msg":"正宗中出即飛<br />\n屌完人又不負責任"},{"pid":"3be5ad5aa8437edd5a621ec56432142ef6f20489","tid":841632,"uid":204946,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T22:59:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2227d73682b5ea477ef829893bfa7f5ecca2c316","tid":841632,"uid":204946,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T22:59:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a45fd1edc37c4b4d5423451c230ece212128c510","tid":841632,"uid":34623,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T23:05:10.000Z","msg":"冇咗美軍基地 中國最撚開心"},{"pid":"f1373ee2e18a23f993540204edbbbcc5eaa7d6de","tid":841632,"uid":53687,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"b1beeca337ce5c831895cee2947d2ec248f697e9","tid":841632,"uid":51701,"like":29,"dislike":4,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T22:15:07.000Z","msg":"負皮做乜鳩<br />\n根本沖繩人真係食晒軍營衰野而冇[補償]<br />\n日軍仲迫過佢地自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n夾係中間真係<img src=\"/ass